  <name>Trimir Journal</name>
  <summary>Journaling, Logging and Activity Tracking</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Trimir Journal is a text diary to help log and in retrospect evaluate all of your experiences, thoughts and ideas as well as your (sports) activities.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Write journal log entries with emoij and hashtags (i.e. üòéÔ∏è #elementary)</li>
      <li>Filter journal entries by clicking on hashtag link</li>
      <li>Render line chart when filtering for "metric tags", i.e. a hashtag followed by a number with optional unit (e.g. "#Trailrun 5km")</li>
      <li>Search journal log entries</li>
      <li>Backup and restore journal to and from JSON file compatible with "ZenJournal - Minimalist Diary" (a 3rd party Android and iOS App; not affiliated)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
